<section class="" id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3 text-center">
                <h2 class="section-heading">About</h2>
                <hr class="dark">
                <p class="">Jessica Sharman is a professional songwriter, topliner, producer and musician.</p>

                <p>Her songs have been used worldwide for film (<span class="italic">The Inbetweeners 2</span>), TV (<span class="italic">Made In Chelsea, Saving Hope</span>) and advertising (<span class="italic">Burberry</span>).</p>

                <p>She's had multiple radio plays, including consecutive weeks spent on Radio 2's A list (<span class="italic">Carry You Home</span>, Ward Thomas). She also co-wrote over a third of the Ward Thomas’ second album <span class="italic">Cartwheels</span>, which went straight to Number 1 making UK Music History by being the first Country album to reach top of the charts.</p>

                <p>She works from her studio in London and has close ties to the music industry in Nashville and LA.</p>

                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="mixer">
    


</section>

<section id="listen">
  <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
              <h2 class="section-heading">Listen</h2>
              <hr class="primary">
          </div>
      </div>
           
      <div id="effect-1" class="row effects clearfix">
      <% @albums.each do |album| %>
        
        <div class="img">
        
          <%= image_tag(album.image.thumb, :alt => 'Album image', :class =>"img-fluid") %>
          
              <div class="overlay">
                
                <h4><%= album.artist %>:</h4>

                <div class="white">
                 <% album.tracks.each do |t| %>
                   <p class="mb-0">
                    <%= t.name %>
                    
                    <%= "feat. "+t.feat if t.feat? %>
                   
                   </p>
                 <% end %>
                 
                 <%= link_to image_tag('get_it_on_itunes.svg', :alt => "Get it on itunes", :class => "pt-2"), album.itunes_link %>
                </div>
        
                
                <a class="close-overlay hidden">x</a>
              
                  
              </div>
          </div>                
         
        <%end%>

       
      </div>        

    </div>
</section>

